short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quickly see the professor's ratings on the MyUCF search page

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With this extension, you can quickly check out a professor's ratings and reviews right on the MyUCF search page without wasting time bouncing between different sites.

Download the extension and click on the icon on the toolbar to quickly see all the professors ratings and their links from RateMyProfessor.com when searching for class on MyUCF.
